  <brief_title>TGV:Use of the Quick Diagnostic Test of the Influenza and the Infection With RSV by the Paediatric Emergency Unit</brief_title>
  <official_title>Exploratory Study of the Use of the Quick Diagnostic Test of the Influenza and the Infection With RSV by the Paediatric Emergency Unit and Their Impact on the Assumption of Responsibility of the Suspect Children of a Viral Infection</official_title>
