  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the impact of the use of a quick diagnostic test of
      infection with RSV and influenza virus on the assumption of clinical responsibility of the
      children consulting at the Paediatric Emergency Unit.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
